summary:
This linkedin account’s purpose is not only to connect with the current members of E.S.T Fellenoord, but also with old members and keep these valuable contacts in its network. Please be informed about the existence of the so called “Vriend van Fellenoord” group. This group receives on an annual basis a yearbook, information about this association and an invitation to a yearly reunion with the other old-members. 

E.S.T. Fellenoord the association:
Eindhoven's Student Tennis-association Fellenoord is a lively sports association with approximately 430 members, at which you can be engaged in activities both on and next to the tennis courts. This makes E.S.T. Fellenoord currently the biggest student sports association in Eindhoven! 

Fellenoord organizes many different activities, both sport oriented as for relaxation and fun. Many activities, on and next to the court, are organized throughout the year by several committees. These consist of a healthy mix of younger and older members, and are always looking for new talents. This is not only useful for nice and meaningful experiences, but it also offers a lot of fun and a great opportunity to make new friends. However, Fellenoord is also available for people who “just want to play tennis”. Our licensed trainers will do everything they can to lift your tennis skills to a (even) higher level, and are always open to your own comments and ideas. For more information, membership details and activities we refer to our website.
